Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:15.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to shine on you,\Nand always like that dazzling sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:18.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will defend you\Nfrom all the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:24.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.72,0:00:39.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If only our hearts could connect,\NI could get you to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:46.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can't\Nsee it now, don't lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:54.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your kindness won't be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:01:01.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be carried aloft by the wind\Nto somewhere that isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:08.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll cross the sea and cross time,\Nand I know you'll blossom one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:15.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the day,\NI'll be there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:22.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I can watch over you\Nlike the sun for all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:32.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:04.69,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 6\NTo Die in the Misty Blue
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.13,0:02:49.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now I look nothing at all like a prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:20.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that you'll be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:21.73,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Torogai?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:31.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to leave with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:35.34,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master, where did you\Nget that donkey?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:38.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to build up his legs\Nuntil he's good and sturdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:40.72,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell your uncle I said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:43.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:44.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:02.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure that you\Ndon't catch cold. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:10.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get yourself killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:15.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:23.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you stand there paralyzed\Nby your lingering affections...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:27.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...the more their chances\Nof dying increase!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:29.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:35.30,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At that pace,\NI doubt that they'll make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.30,0:04:38.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...to the Misty Blue Pass\Nbefore the sun goes down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:59.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have 100 men between her last\Nknown location and Yashiro village...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:02.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and 350 men on\Neach of the mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:04.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...that divide the Aoyumi\Ninto east and west.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They have been ordered\Nto search for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:11.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reports suggest that the woman\Nappears to be gravely injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:14.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do not believe that\Nlocating her will prove difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:16.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you so certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:17.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.51,0:05:18.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have a report, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:23.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have had reports\Nfrom the Yashiro village area...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:28.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...that last night some farmers saw\Nwhat appeared to be a Kanbal woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:30.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What direction was\Nthis woman headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:34.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As for that... Some farmers claimed\Nthat she was traveling to the west...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:36.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...while other reports say\Nthat she was heading south.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:39.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's doubling back\Ntowards Kosenkyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:44.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've located her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:46.04,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:48.58,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are reports of a\Nsuspicious-looking woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:51.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...being spotted in the lands\Neast of the Yakoo rice terraces.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:53.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To the east this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:06:00.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Send the men who left\Nto join the manhunt to the east!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:04.73,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, to the west as well! And assign\Nlookouts to Kosenkyo's city gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:05.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:07.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:08.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:18.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the woman anticipated\Nthat there would be a manhunt for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:21.74,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These multiple sightings\Nare most likely a diversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:23.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you two think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:26.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe them to be\Na diversion as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:27.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I concur.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:29.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:32.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that to be the case as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:37.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I ordered you\Nto get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:41.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lying still doing nothing\Nonly frustrates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:45.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it only slows down\Nthe healing process.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:50.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is but one option\Nleft open to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:53.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that is to deduce\Nwhat that woman is thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:55.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We put ourselves in her place...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:58.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and we deduce what action\Nshe is likely to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:01.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I am physically incompetent...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:03.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but my mind is in\Nperfect working order!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:08.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Taga and Sune, gather the intelligence\Nthat has come to the manhunt teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:09.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:15.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zen, Yun, and Jin, the rest of us\Nwill analyze that woman's thoughts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:16.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:26.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The first order of business is\Nto counter the woman's next ploy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:28.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...with a certain and resolute\Nmove of our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:32.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let us determine what path\Nthe woman is taking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:35.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Begin silent meditation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:41.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About those hunting dogs\Nthat attacked us both...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:47.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As you say, surely there can't be\Na great number of men of that caliber.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:50.73,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That said, those people are tenacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:53.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They'll keep coming and coming\Nuntil that boy is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:57.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:08:01.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can manage to give them the slip,\Nyou'll live to see the next spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:07.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chances are, that egg\Nwon't hatch anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.79,0:08:13.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eggs don't hatch until what's inside\Nhas developed to a certain degree...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:17.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and is fully prepared to emerge\Nand face the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:23.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From what I saw, the egg inside you\Nhasn't finished its preparations yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:26.74,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will go and find us some answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:29.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure that you\Nget away safely, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck to your own task, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:35.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magmmmm
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:13.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:28.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The north. The woman will\Ncross the Misty Blue Mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:29.77,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My conclusion was north as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:32.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She was born in Kanbal.\NShe will go north.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:37.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but she is wounded.\NAnd that wound is no mere scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.27,0:09:39.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And most importantly,\Nthe prince is with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:41.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At a glance, it certainly appears\Nto be a suicidal move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:44.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A wise man would avoid\Nthe Misty Blue Mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:48.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is the conclusion that\Nshe expects us to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:52.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She will do the opposite and\Nwill go to the Misty Blue Mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.39,0:09:53.72,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.06,0:09:57.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Misdirection is commonly employed\Nby any skilled tactician.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:10:00.46,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True. During our skirmish,\Nshe feigned escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:04.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She also discarded her spear and\Ninstead attacked with a throwing stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:06.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She misled us both times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:10.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you could say she merely used\Nany means necessary for her goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:12.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is one thing\Nthat does concern me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:16.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That she refused to strike\Nany of us with a fatal blow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:21.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Under those circumstances,\Nwe all could have been struck dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:29.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that was another case of subterfuge\Nmeant to throw us into confusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:32.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...then it is entirely possible that\Nshe will double back and go south.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:35.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:39.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That detail has troubled me\Never since the battle as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:43.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a woman who will stop\Nat nothing to escape with the prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:46.34,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...so why is it that she did not kill us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:52.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surely that would have been the\Nsoundest course of action, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:55.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is most baffling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:58.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, I think there was some other\Nmotive at work behind that action...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:11:02.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...that is separate from her objective\Nof escaping with the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:06.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In which case,\Nthe woman's destination is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:07.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:10.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The manhunt teams have\Nreceived reports of a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:14.24,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...resembling a Kanbal native\Nheading west on the Tosei highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:16.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is a diversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:18.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We just concluded that she is\Ngoing to the Misty Blue Mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:22.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But sir, they say that she is carrying\Nwhat appears to be a short spear...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:25.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and, what is most noteworthy,\Nshe has a child in tow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:34.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well played. Not only has that woman\Ndivided the manhunt's forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:38.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...she's also kept us pinned down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:43.03,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moribito Guardian of the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:56.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:58.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:01.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:10.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did I tell you? Aren't you glad\Nwe didn't join the manhunt teams?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:14.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I knew all along that\Nshe was going to go west.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:30.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Commander! Please, follow the path\Nthat you believe to be best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:33.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will take Taga with me and\Nscour the road to the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:35.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:38.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go. You're in no condition to ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:40.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:43.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She may be our enemy,\Nbut I admire this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:47.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If the woman on the road\Ndoes indeed turn out to be her...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:50.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...use blowgun darts\Ndipped in poison to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:54.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you do,\Ndon't get inside her striking range.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:55.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:57.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:00.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You and I will make for\Nthe Misty Blue Mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:14.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:16.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:20.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Has a woman been by here?\NAn injured woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:25.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, plenty of them.\NBecause of my profession, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:26.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But every woman I receive is gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:29.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...the moment their business\Nwith me is concluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:31.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:34.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why come to me unless\Nthey need medicinal herbs?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.34,0:13:40.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even a man like me knows that\Nit's a man's role to keep women safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:43.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But for as long as I can remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:46.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...it's the girl who's always gotten\Nherself hurt and always ends up here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:48.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...so what can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:51.73,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder my first thought is\Nalways to heal her wounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:53.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:58.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive us. Perhaps our\Nquestion was inappropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:07.04,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:11.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The front hoof prints aren't\Nthe same size as the back ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:12.68,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Kokkou stallion, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:16.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even a horse that can gallop\Nacross three kingdoms in one night...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:17.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...is of no use if you don't let it run.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.06,0:14:25.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We shall capture them before nightfall!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:26.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:43.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The mountains seem\Nfarther away than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:46.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kanbal really that far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.75,0:14:50.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kanbal lies beyond the mountains\Nbeyond that mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:52.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:56.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.26,0:15:00.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:04.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What sort of place is Kanbal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:09.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to Yogo, it's a harsh place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:13.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The air is thin there,\Nand the soil is rocky and barren.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:18.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But there are meadows where\Nyou can give free rein to your horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:21.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're there,\Nit's not such a bad place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:24.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Does your family live there, Balsa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:31.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:53.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cut across the stream!\NThe paths branch off for a while, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:55.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...there's an outcropping ahead\Nwhere you can get back onto this trail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:58.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever it takes\Nto get there ahead of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:15:59.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:21.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:51.04,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:24.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have you now, Spear-wielder!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:35.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:43.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:45.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But the prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:51.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, sir! But we can't\Nafford to have you die here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:24.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure that a horse like that would\Nbe able to climb back up on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:26.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:23.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This arrived from the Hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:43.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When the time is right,\NI shall inform the mikado myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.81,0:20:45.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You may go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:46.44,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:04.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Shuga!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.46,0:21:11.60,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Shuga, this is for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:14.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.47,0:22:25.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You said you'd gore me to death\Nif I followed you, so I could only wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.14,0:22:28.74,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What am I, a warrior's wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:36.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, I see you're still\Nin one piece, Balsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.15,0:22:39.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:43.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For now, though,\NI just want to get a little sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.72,0:23:13.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As I sat huddled and alone, holding\Nback the tears on those nights...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:20.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When it felt like I was about\Nto succumb to my doubts...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.20,0:23:25.47,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...there you were,\Nat my side before I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:32.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was none other than you\Nwho was there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:47.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I keep wishing, "I want to be strong."\NI stumble and hurt myself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.09,0:23:56.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But because I have you to believe in,\NI can get back to my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:24:03.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I simply want to tell\Nmy dear one, "Thank you. "
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.24,0:24:08.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the top of my lungs,\Nagain and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.38,0:24:16.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I call out to my precious loved one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:20.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is my voice reaching you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.96,0:24:29.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In this world that always changes,\Nhuman warmth never does.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.20,0:24:39.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain I sensed the presence\Nof the one that I hold dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.01,0:24:45.01,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.51,0:24:45.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum tries to acclimate himself\Nto the life of a commoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.81,0:24:49.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A vague sense of unease\Nbegins to blossom in his young heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.42,0:24:52.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time,\N"Chagum's Resolve."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.02,0:24:57.03,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 7\NChagum's Resolve
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.29,0:24:54.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The waterwheel turns...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.46,0:24:56.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...carrying his emotions with it.
